oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Variety of Live Chet Atkins' Tracks
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording features a number of tracks performed by an unidentified live show. The recording features segments performed by Chet Atkins (musician) and the Prairie Playboys (musical group). The recordings are from a variety of unidentified dates.
